title: Reward Claimed: GTA$500,000
headline: Reward Claimed: GTA$500,000
subtitle: Thanks For Participating In Stunt Week!
content:
An issue has been identified with the delivery of the GTA$500,000 Stunt Jump bonus.

Instead, a bonus Reward of GTA$500,000 has been deposited into your Maze Bank Account for participating in Stunt Week.

Stay tuned to the Rockstar Newswire for more limited-time events coming soon to GTA Online.
